179 (6) Report. The committee shall adopt specific findings or recommendations that
180 include proposed legislation, and the chairperson shall file a report of the same prior to
181 the date of abolishment specified in this resolution.
182 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 1, 2025.
